{"hash":"1beb66ec8d503408f3eb621923bd75e91e25d200","data":{"post":{"title":"Elysium Extra 1.1 Released","path":"/elysium-extra-1-1-released/","displayDate":"5 November 2014","date":"2014-11-05T00:00:00+00:00","dateModified":null,"timeToRead":4,"author":"Muhammad Rehan Saeed","headings":[{"value":"The Future of WPF"},{"value":"What's New"},{"value":"Theming Support"},{"value":"Performance"},{"value":"Whats Next"}],"tags":[{"id":".NET","title":".NET","path":"/tag/net/"},{"id":"C#","title":"C#","path":"/tag/c/"},{"id":"Elysium","title":"Elysium","path":"/tag/elysium/"},{"id":"Elysium Extra","title":"Elysium Extra","path":"/tag/elysium-extra/"},{"id":"Metro","title":"Metro","path":"/tag/metro/"},{"id":"Modern","title":"Modern","path":"/tag/modern/"},{"id":"UI","title":"UI","path":"/tag/ui/"},{"id":"User Interface","title":"User Interface","path":"/tag/user-interface/"},{"id":"Windows Presentation Foundation","title":"Windows Presentation Foundation","path":"/tag/windows-presentation-foundation/"},{"id":"WPF","title":"WPF","path":"/tag/wpf/"}],"description":"Elysium Extra Version 1.1 is a Windows Presentation Foundation (WPF) SDK providing Metro styles for built in WPF controls and some custom controls.","content":"<div style=\"width: 100%; margin: 25px 0 25px 0;\">\n    <div style=\"position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; padding-top: 25px; height: 0;\">\n        <iframe style=\"position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;\"\n            src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/PGM_uBy99GA\"\n            allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen>\n        </iframe>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<p>Version 1.1.4 of Elysium Extra has just been released! If you've never heard of it, Elysium Extra is a Windows Presentation Foundation (WPF) SDK which provides a wide variety of controls and styles. Here are the relevant links to get started with the project:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/wpf-metro-part4-elysium-extra/\">Review</a> - A comprehensive review of the controls and styles available.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/RehanSaeed/Elysium-Extra\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">GitHub</a> - The home of the Elysium Extra project. Hosted on GitHub. Submit issues, ask questions and view source code.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/RehanSaeed/Elysium-Extra\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Getting Started</a> - A quick start guide to using Elysium Extra in your WPF project.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.nuget.org/packages/Elysium.Extra\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">NuGet</a> - The Elysium Extra NuGet package link.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 447 70' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-876646095087a8570b8a7dc5a80c0ebe'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-876646095087a8570b8a7dc5a80c0ebe)' width='447' height='70' xlink:href='data:image/png%3bbase64%2ciVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAEAAAAAKCAYAAAAEqljUAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAEBklEQVRIx%2bVW2VIbVxDVJ5AqB60jzYwACRAjAaYw2AaHSAItIEtIAi0MQrZkwMgUJuXEIWYLUHFl%2bQgeeeCf8pZvSNk66b6jIQPGjvPshy507%2b31dPcZbJeXl3%2bdnJzg9PS0TYIvRN6fnZ3h4uLiTxsX39XV1Xa5XHA6nSQOOBwfCr/ddn9Tx5RP2X2uL4fD%2bVF75ydzsJwdH9pzrVzz0dERbNx5vvD71bYkSfB6vfD5fJBlGarqh6IoQjwej7g3zyx8Nu9Y3%2b12C3u320P%2b/GSvgn2aOnxmPdaROz74TlFk8VdV//XNOoYvF9mYep24nKMsX7uz2kkk1lhmfqYO5dbmXA8PD98zAAIVRVGhhcMIDfajt7cX/h6/QNIAQ8HI6F30BwIiuCiAHAaD/QjSnZeKDAwMYm4uhtHxe4hHv4W9uxsuCjKkhdEfDHaKcZPvPkRGhuHnYsmHh%2b4UAtrjcZNIV6CGQiFo2jBS6TQCPYoA1SxIC0cQ6g/CLZpiFGw2bmAwhLA2JIBTqQnsh%2b24IQIgyQCEJ4UAEBOA7u47lOQIfv/1D7ze28PZ6Vs0G6uYjc1AFgFkNDZbaD7VsbnVQj6fR7lUROPZcyw9nodebyD%2baArVWgVj9yag62vQKJHJ%2bxM4ePsb6ms1klXoqzqSqRQ2d3aQSc1icamKlZUSStUVbLS2sfvyBYGswm734fTnX5BKRJEvlDGfiGMxv4ilchX